 perform the Witr prayer, O people of the Quran!\u201d Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThe Witr\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11580,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/22\/dua-salat-ala-al-nabi-most\/","url_meta":{"origin":12941,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salawat: Nearest to Prophet blessed him most","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe closest of people to me on the Day of Resurrection are those who sent the most blessings upon me.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 484 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33674,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/02\/12-rakaat-al-sunan-al-rawatib\/","url_meta":{"origin":12941,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sunnah: Twelve raka\u2019at of al-Sunan al-Rawatib prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 2, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever perseveres in performing twelve cycles